---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Container } from "@/components/layout/Container";
import HeroImage from "../components/ui/HeroImage.astro";
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout
    title="Steps to Opening a Daycare | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Your path to opening a daycare depends on your state's licensing process and local requirements. Understand what affects your timeline and approach."
>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <HeroImage
                src="/images/startup/steps-to-opening-a-daycare.webp"
                alt="Strategic roadmap checklist displaying the critical steps to opening a childcare center"
                className="mb-4 md:mb-12"
            />
            <div class="text-center">
                <span class="pro-text-meta mb-2 block">
                    The Journey
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6">
                    YOUR Path to Opening
                </h1>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    Opening a daycare involves navigating state licensing, local regulations, and market preparation. The timeline of your journey depends on where you're opening.
                </p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- FACTORS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section bg-gray-50/50">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card mb-3 md:mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    What Affects Your Timeline
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Some states have streamlined licensing taking weeks, while others involve months of paperwork and inspections. The type of facility—home-based versus center-based—triggers completely different pathways.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Your existing situation matters too. Do you already have a suitable space or need to find one? Each of these factors changes which obstacles you'll face.
                    </p>
                    <p class="hidden md:block">
                        Local requirements layer on top of state regulations. Fire marshal inspections, health department approvals, and zoning clearances all have their own prerequisites.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- WHY GENERIC FAILS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Why Advice Conflicts
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Generic timelines fall apart when they hit your specific reality. An article that says "getting licensed takes 3 months" might be right for one state and completely wrong for yours.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The order of operations is determined by your state's licensing agency. Following the wrong sequence means redoing work or missing deadlines.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card text-center border-2 border-teal-200/50 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/20 to-white/50">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-4">
                    Map YOUR Success Path
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-3 md:mb-6">
                    Before planning your path, understand your income potential based on your state's regulations.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/#calculator"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-2 md:px-8 md:py-4 shadow-lg transition-all text-xs md:text-base group"
                >
                    Use the Free Calculator
                    <ArrowRight className="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
